  "difficultyLevel": 5,
  "lyrics": "🎵\n🎵 Debatable, unforgettable, debatable, yeah unforgettable 🎵\n🎵 See perception is kindness, perception is your mind, perception is you, understanding you, yeah 🎵\n🎵 Unforgettable, can you forget you? For just one day, yeah yeah yeah 🎵\n🎵 Unforgettable, BE unforgettable and behave in your way 🎵\n🎵lights, all above me, all I see is mine 🎵\n🎵 Can't walk me down the line of envy and see you here 🎵\n🎵 Differently in the pocket of disaster, are you feeling what you remember? 🎵\n🎵 You're unforgettable, you're undeniable, when you do the diabolical and see your wings fly with mine 🎵\n🎵 You're unforgettable, undeniable, unbreakable inside of all that you feel, oh yeah 🎵\n🎵 Don't change, don't rearrange, only put yourself in the blame of maintain\n 🎵\n🎵 Damn, gotta make change for you, gotta be the thing that you want me to be 🎵\n🎵 so you don't forget about me 🎵\n🎵\n🎵 You're unforgettable, you're just cannibalizing your own dreams 🎵\n🎵 You're deniable, agreeable, fake front now you know 🎵\n🎵 It's just schemes in your mind, oh are you mine? 🎵\n🎵 Do you mind a little change for me? Oh no, no, no, no, not for you 🎵\n🎵 You're unforgettable, you're unforgettable 🎵\n🎵 Baby fly, past your own line, so I remember why I'm all alone 🎵\n🎵 Disaster on the phone telling me you're inner thoughts, I can see the sleep that you lack between the mes 🎵\n🎵 You're unforgettable, undeniable, unquestionably you're unforgetting 🎵\n🎵 Pull up your own way, please dont judge of highways 🎵\n🎵 Undeniably hot and insane, too much in my main vein 🎵\n🎵 Unforgettable, forget me, yeah unforgettable, I'm just trying to feel my way to the next high, yeah 🎵\nCan we get high? I mean, that'd be fun. Can we? Can we?\nIt'd make this night unforgettable.",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 10.920000076293945,
      "text": "🎵",
      "start": 10.220000267028809
    },
    {
      "end": 15.079999923706055,
      "text": "🎵 Debatable, unforgettable, debatable, yeah unforgettable 🎵",
      "start": 10.920000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 21.68000030517578,
      "text": "🎵 See perception is kindness, perception is your mind, perception is you, understanding you, yeah 🎵",
      "start": 15.079999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 26.6200008392334,
      "text": "🎵 Unforgettable, can you forget you? For just one day, yeah yeah yeah 🎵",
      "start": 21.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 32.2400016784668,
      "text": "🎵 Unforgettable, BE unforgettable and behave in your way 🎵",
      "start": 26.6200008392334
    },
    {
      "end": 39.63999938964844,
      "text": "🎵lights, all above me, all I see is mine 🎵",
      "start": 32.2400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 45.7400016784668,
      "text": "🎵 Can't walk me down the line of envy and see you here 🎵",
      "start": 39.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 53.52000045776367,
      "text": "🎵 Differently in the pocket of disaster, are you feeling what you remember? 🎵",
      "start": 45.7400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 63.41999816894531,
      "text": "🎵 You're unforgettable, you're undeniable, when you do the diabolical and see your wings fly with mine 🎵",
      "start": 53.52000045776367
    },
    {
      "end": 74.58000183105469,
      "text": "🎵 You're unforgettable, undeniable, unbreakable inside of all that you feel, oh yeah 🎵",
      "start": 63.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 86.69999694824219,
      "text": "🎵 Don't change, don't rearrange, only put yourself in the blame of maintain\n 🎵",
      "start": 74.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 92.66000366210938,
      "text": "🎵 Damn, gotta make change for you, gotta be the thing that you want me to be 🎵",
      "start": 86.69999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 97.19999694824219,
      "text": "🎵 so you don't forget about me 🎵",
      "start": 92.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 107.58000183105469,
      "text": "🎵",
      "start": 106.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 112.23999786376953,
      "text": "🎵 You're unforgettable, you're just cannibalizing your own dreams 🎵",
      "start": 107.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 117.12000274658203,
      "text": "🎵 You're deniable, agreeable, fake front now you know 🎵",
      "start": 112.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 123.12000274658203,
      "text": "🎵 It's just schemes in your mind, oh are you mine? 🎵",
      "start": 117.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 127.95999908447266,
      "text": "🎵 Do you mind a little change for me? Oh no, no, no, no, not for you 🎵",
      "start": 123.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 138.66000366210938,
      "text": "🎵 You're unforgettable, you're unforgettable 🎵",
      "start": 127.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 152.97999572753906,
      "text": "🎵 Baby fly, past your own line, so I remember why I'm all alone 🎵",
      "start": 138.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 160.66000366210938,
      "text": "🎵 Disaster on the phone telling me you're inner thoughts, I can see the sleep that you lack between the mes 🎵",
      "start": 152.97999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 175.39999389648438,
      "text": "🎵 You're unforgettable, undeniable, unquestionably you're unforgetting 🎵",
      "start": 160.9600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 181.9600067138672,
      "text": "🎵 Pull up your own way, please dont judge of highways 🎵",
      "start": 175.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 194.67999267578125,
      "text": "🎵 Undeniably hot and insane, too much in my main vein 🎵",
      "start": 186.8800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 204.33999633789062,
      "text": "🎵 Unforgettable, forget me, yeah unforgettable, I'm just trying to feel my way to the next high, yeah 🎵",
      "start": 194.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 210.5,
      "text": "Can we get high? I mean, that'd be fun. Can we? Can we?",
      "start": 205.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 212,
      "text": "It'd make this night unforgettable.",
      "start": 210.5
    }
  ],
